# Access list for minqlx (admins / mods / bans).
#
# Copy this file to access.txt and add your own entries.
# Be sure to run /reload_access if editing this file while the server is running.
# The server will overwrite your changes on map exit and shutdown, so edit it
# via in-game commands (!admin, !mod, !ban) once the server is up.
#
# 1 entry per line, format: steamid|(mod|admin|ban)
# ex: 76561198072786081|ban
00000000000000000|admin
